</div></div></div></div></div></div> </header><nav id="site-menus" class="site-menus"><div id="site-menus-main-menu"><div id="main-menu" class="region region-main-menu main-menu"><div id="block-system-main-menu" class="block block-system block-menu"><h4 class="block-title">Main menu</h4><div class="content"><ul class="menu"><li class="first leaf"><a href="/news-opinion">News</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/sport">Sport</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/business">Business</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/technology">Technology</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="http://www.theweek.co.uk/motoring">Cars</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/taxonomy/term/60913"> Money</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="http://www.theweek.co.uk/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="/the-week-unwrapped">Podcast</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="http://subscription.theweek.co.uk/subscribe?utm_source=theweek.co.uk&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=brandsite&amp;utm_content=menu-link-red" class="subscriptions" style="color: #c00;">Subscriptions</a></li><li class="last leaf"><a href="https://www.theweeksociety.co.uk/offers?utm_source=theweek.co.uk&amp;utm_medium=redirect&amp;utm_campaign=TWS_redirect" target="_blank">Offers</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div id="site-menus-secondary-menu"><div id="secondary-menu" class="region region-secondary-menu secondary-menu"><div id="block-menu-menu-sections-menu" class="block block-menu"><p class="block-title">Sections</p></div><div id="block-menu-secondary-menu" class="block block-menu"><p class="block-title">Secondary menu</p><div class="content"><ul class="menu"><li class="first leaf"><a href="http://www.theweek.co.uk/brexit-0">Brexit</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="http://www.theweek.co.uk/donald-trump">Donald Trump</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="http://www.theweek.co.uk/78595/kensington-palace-inside-prince-harry-and-meghan-markle-s-london-home">Kensington Palace</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="http://www.theweek.co.uk/cultural-appropriation">Cultural appropriation</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="http://www.theweek.co.uk/london-house-prices">House prices</a></li><li class="last leaf"><a href="http://www.theweek.co.uk/theweekday">Email newsletter sign-up</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></nav><div id="page" class="page"><div id="preface-top" class="region region-preface-top preface-top"><div id="block-dfp-billboard-leaderboard" class="block block-dfp"><div class="content"><div id="dfp-ad-billboard_leaderboard-wrapper" class="dfp-tag-wrapper"><div id="dfp-ad-billboard_leaderboard" class="dfp-tag-wrapper"><div class="slug">Advertisement</div>
