</div></div></div></li><li class="even"><div class="node node-article node-promoted node-teaser even node-teaser"><div class="content"><div class="teaser-image"> <a href="/brexit/95003/chequers-plan-explained-brexit-white-paper"><img src="http://cdn1.theweek.co.uk/sites/theweek/files/styles/1x1_100/public/2017/09/bojo1.jpg?itok=skxOzor3" alt="Boris Johnson and Theresa May at cabinet" title="Boris Johnson and Theresa May at cabinet" /></a></div><div class="field field-name-kicker field-label-inline"><div class="field-items"><a href="/brexit-0">Brexit</a></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-published-date field-type-datetime field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><span class="date-display-single">10 Sep, 2018</span></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-short-title field-type-text field-label-hidden"><h2 class="field-item even title"><a href="/brexit/95003/chequers-plan-explained-brexit-white-paper" class="combined-link teaser-title title" title="Why the Chequers plan threatens to split Tories" rel="">Why the Chequers plan threatens to split Tories</a></h2></div><p class="short-teaser">Former Brexit minister Steve Baker claims Conservative MPs planning Brexit revolt</p></div></div></li><li class="odd"><div class="node node-article node-promoted node-teaser odd node-teaser"><div class="content"><div class="teaser-image"> <a href="/premier-league/96301/premier-league-brexit-english-football-top-flight-exemption"><img src="http://cdn2.theweek.co.uk/sites/theweek/files/styles/1x1_100/public/2018/09/riyad_mahrez_ngolo_kante_gettyimages-614803330.jpg?itok=pAezQJpp" alt="Riyad Mahrez NGolo Kante Brexit" title="Riyad Mahrez NGolo Kante Brexit" /></a></div><div class="field field-name-kicker field-label-inline"><div class="field-items"><a href="/premier-league">Premier League</a></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-published-date field-type-datetime field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="fie